WD Simple Login
=====================

WD Simple Login is a simple login system, built for security and flexibility. It is built to allow for user login, new user registration, password retrieval and successful login confirmation all within one page! Utilizing just JavaScript and no external libraries, this simple login script is built for speed.

WD Simple Login is MIT-licensed so you can use it however you like for free.

Contents
=============

* README
* index.php
* class.database.php - Database object to connect to the database
* class.validate.php - Validation object for login, registration, etc.
* style.css - Primary stylesheet
* wd-simple-login-db.sql - Initial sql to set the database defaults

